starvationevasion.client.MegaMawile.model

Class _Statistics

  • java.lang.Object
    • starvationevasion.client.MegaMawile.model._Statistics

  • public class _Statistics
extends java.lang.Object
    Class receives data from the game client and then populates this class with all the statistics from the regions of the world. Any two clients playing the same game should have there own copies of this data but the data should be identical, only the server/simulator should be populating this class otherwise the data is read-only.
